{"tid":863602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港島四大水塘歷史性冠絕全球 或符合世界文化遺產資格","createTime":"2018-10-15T17:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T09:47:13.000Z","uid":82640,"like":311,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"db366869ad79899d00a0297380ce364c3506b4f2","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"最近留意到近10年好多世界文化遺產都係以量去增強個珍貴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近嘅有澳門歷史城區（全部未裝修前衰過香港法定古蹟中嘅西式大樓任何一座，將佢地擺埋先突出個罕有性；為申報世界文化遺產先裝修返到現時咁）<br />\n亞洲內仲有韓國堆寺廟群同日本明治維新堆工業建設（只係1880年至1900年代）<br />\n最垃圾級嘅仲有齋吹水吹到世界級嘅新加坡植物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講法香港島四大水塘群點會唔符合資格做世界文化遺產先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先講下成為世界文化遺產有咩資格...<br />\n<br />\n// 提名的文化遺產必須具有『突出的普世價值』以及至少滿足以下十項基準之一：<br />\n（i）表現人類創造力的經典之作。<br />\n（ii）在某期間或某種文化圈裏對建築、技術、紀念性藝術、城鎮規劃、景觀設計之發展有巨大影響，促進人類價值的交流。<br />\n（iii）呈現有關現存或者已經消失的文化傳統、文明的獨特或稀有之證據。<br />\n（iv）關於呈現人類歷史重要階段的建築類型，或者建築及技術的組合，或者景觀上的卓越典範。<br />\n（v）代表某一個或數個文化的人類傳統聚落或土地使用，提供出色的典範－特別是因為難以抗拒的歷史潮流而處於消滅危機的場合。<br />\n（vi）具有顯著普遍價值的事件、活的傳統、理念、信仰、藝術及文學作品，有直接或實質的連結（世界遺產委員會認為該基準應最好與其他基準共同使用）。 //<br />\n<br />\n基本上除咗（iii）之外都有幾會符合到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一個賣點係當中三大水塘仍在服役<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更加難得<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港島四大水塘</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yes-news.com/201601/o3klGTjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2F201601%2Fo3klGTjb.jpg&h=b917078f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薄扶林水塘：1863年竣工，有6項設施被列為古蹟，當中3項為法定古蹟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/aa/Dam_%281917%29_of_the_Tai_Tam_Tuk_Reservoir_03.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Faa%2FDam_%25281917%2529_of_the_Tai_Tam_Tuk_Reservoir_03.JPG&h=c225f47c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大潭水塘：1888年首期竣工，有27項設施被列為古蹟，當中22項為法定古蹟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ssl.c.photoshelter.com/img-get/I0000C0Me7Sw8NjI/s/900/720/HK-MG-0273.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fssl.c.photoshelter.com%2Fimg-get%2FI0000C0Me7Sw8NjI%2Fs%2F900%2F720%2FHK-MG-0273.jpg&h=c915dc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃泥涌水塘：1899年竣工，有5項設施被列為古蹟，當中4項為法定古蹟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20161217/large/17fa25p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20161217%2Flarge%2F17fa25p.jpg&h=1f370b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港仔水塘：1890年首期竣工，有8項設施被列為古蹟，當中4項為法定古蹟。<br />\n<br />\n本身已經好多係法定古蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係文獻同價值方向唔係問題<br />\n只需要將佢地嘅故事用返論文貫穿返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成為世界文化遺產只係時間問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ac2c79a2627fbd239a290e421f77dd470b3344","tid":863602,"uid":5205,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"世界文化遺產係用黎搵錢 <br />\n香港想用個啲地方搵錢咪比人污染曬"},{"pid":"93e784fe5f606a921bc3bdae7736d181de870570","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":166,"dislike":0,"score":166,"quote":{"pid":"04ac2c79a2627fbd239a290e421f77dd470b3344","tid":863602,"uid":5205,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"世界文化遺產係用黎搵錢 <br />\n香港想用個啲地方搵錢咪比人污染曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"你有冇諗過好多人想鏟平啲水塘<br />\n做咗世遺有價值大條道理唔可以鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285e44aba4c1f90d27c5f5a3c322261732c6e3da","tid":863602,"uid":39181,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"19世紀既野仲用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd331e993e2eac6674d6efc2a34879a883514c4","tid":863602,"uid":115441,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"呢d真係應該留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3ecf4a3f63ebc257957da5d9035439aae638bd","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"quote":{"pid":"285e44aba4c1f90d27c5f5a3c322261732c6e3da","tid":863602,"uid":39181,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"19世紀既野仲用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"好多水塘可以用幾百年<br />\n但好似香港長年為水而搏鬥不停建設<br />\n就好獨特稀有<br />\n係香港世代嘅一部分"},{"pid":"e056915332a6586035be21218fda58ae1e7f5986","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家都可以關注一下香港嘅古蹟保育問題"},{"pid":"eb5849a955ecf2a94b6f33acd3c29dbbe8634a9e","tid":863602,"uid":117200,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"政府仲想呢幾年拆左佢起新移民樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快香港連行山都無得行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2193afc8b782efa11eb36edf2efdb9130d417d","tid":863602,"uid":58670,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"古蹟只包建築，唔包成個建築群，吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcef41f3a06efdb626a81497afe84f14acc018a","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"eb5849a955ecf2a94b6f33acd3c29dbbe8634a9e","tid":863602,"uid":117200,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"政府仲想呢幾年拆左佢起新移民樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快香港連行山都無得行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"所以更加要推動世界級認證<br />\n之前都放棄發展申請地質公園<br />\n證明呢啲要世界級虛榮放棄發展上<br />\n港府係可以接受"},{"pid":"89e7ccec103e2a8f90a8e7dfa367077e5cb4d706","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"cc2193afc8b782efa11eb36edf2efdb9130d417d","tid":863602,"uid":58670,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"古蹟只包建築，唔包成個建築群，吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港古蹟分級同世遺個包括範圍有出入架<br />\n如果申請世遺<br />\n應該係四個水塘成個蓄水帶（成個水塘系統）都計入去<br />\n即係包括蓄水渠嘅郊野公園範圍"},{"pid":"d58bc325f0150ff7985e271aa557f2a9b9d974cb","tid":863602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e7ccec103e2a8f90a8e7dfa367077e5cb4d706","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"cc2193afc8b782efa11eb36edf2efdb9130d417d","tid":863602,"uid":58670,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"古蹟只包建築，唔包成個建築群，吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港古蹟分級同世遺個包括範圍有出入架<br />\n如果申請世遺<br />\n應該係四個水塘成個蓄水帶（成個水塘系統）都計入去<br />\n即係包括蓄水渠嘅郊野公園範圍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08673d3e0c22560bffbba0db86a871fa24c78c3f","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"89e7ccec103e2a8f90a8e7dfa367077e5cb4d706","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"cc2193afc8b782efa11eb36edf2efdb9130d417d","tid":863602,"uid":58670,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"古蹟只包建築，唔包成個建築群，吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港古蹟分級同世遺個包括範圍有出入架<br />\n如果申請世遺<br />\n應該係四個水塘成個蓄水帶（成個水塘系統）都計入去<br />\n即係包括蓄水渠嘅郊野公園範圍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"再補充一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以澳門歷史城區（Historic Centre of Macao）為例<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h924yLD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh924yLD.png&h=e8c7c84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要受保護建築係紅色<br />\n藍色係主要受保護範圍<br />\n<br />\n以上兩者換上去四大水塘即係<br />\n水塘建築設施及高架水道係主要受保護建築<br />\n水塘主體及引水道係主要受保護範圍<br />\n呢兩樣可以直接問水務處拎圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粉紅色係緩衝區(Buffer Zones)<br />\n都係唔郁得嘅<br />\n<br />\n四大水塘黎講其實咪即係成個郊野公園囉<br />\n拎哂當初郊野公園點解咁set嘅文件已經解釋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00c8bd6ecdd9487f23a47f594fe75f1efa72612","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d58bc325f0150ff7985e271aa557f2a9b9d974cb","tid":863602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e7ccec103e2a8f90a8e7dfa367077e5cb4d706","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"cc2193afc8b782efa11eb36edf2efdb9130d417d","tid":863602,"uid":58670,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"古蹟只包建築，唔包成個建築群，吹脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港古蹟分級同世遺個包括範圍有出入架<br />\n如果申請世遺<br />\n應該係四個水塘成個蓄水帶（成個水塘系統）都計入去<br />\n即係包括蓄水渠嘅郊野公園範圍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"如果以新加坡植物園圖則做例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fWtgon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fWtgon.png&h=221aa92d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBuffer Zone仲要大過個公園範圍"},{"pid":"540d2103c0e3a635720c1fbc09f0b8b5e3bff0a7","tid":863602,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"港共為左瀨共，隨時拆"},{"pid":"d9dd8a5da5e709793df291379adddbb7d170fe5f","tid":863602,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540d2103c0e3a635720c1fbc09f0b8b5e3bff0a7","tid":863602,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"港共為左瀨共，隨時拆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日行嫁屌"},{"pid":"9ba8a0ff29d6e312395bf07b50d6e30a587a3805","tid":863602,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9dd8a5da5e709793df291379adddbb7d170fe5f","tid":863602,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540d2103c0e3a635720c1fbc09f0b8b5e3bff0a7","tid":863602,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"港共為左瀨共，隨時拆"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日行嫁屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"更加有責任將佢地推上世界文化遺產"},{"pid":"09faf5722057d2ce4ce3c0c3244f25eb5f9c0977","tid":863602,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9dd8a5da5e70